data.description: $10,000 Price Improvement!!  This is the home you've been waiting for! POOL, JACUZZI, RV PARKING, SOLAR, BIKING/WALKING TRAIL!!!! This inviting and TURN-KEY SINGLE-STORY home boasts 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms and is an entertainer's dream!  The living room is in the front of the house and has a cozy wood/gas fireplace with a TV mount above the mantle. The light and bright kitchen with quartz countertops and backsplash overlooks the private and securely fenced backyard pool area so that you won't be left out when you are preparing the goodies for your family and friends.  Enjoy baking in the double oven or cooking on the 5-burner stove with a griddle. Tile throughout the home as well and instant hot water in the kitchen with the under-the-sink, tankless water heater. The pantry has lots of shelves for that extra storage and down the hall, you'll find even more storage and the bedrooms and the guest bath. The first bedroom has a double-door entry. Walk out of your master suite and into your relaxing and private heated jacuzzi right outside of your door.  The pool also can be heated and has a ledge for just hanging out in the 7ft deep end. The backyard is incredibly spacious and private with a tall dense hedge along the entire backyard.  It has two alumawood patio covers,  both wired for electricity, and one is equipped with an outdoor ceiling fan. The low-maintenance backyard is pre-wired for speakers too. The pool has been resurfaced, tile redone and a new light installed a few years ago. Auto-sprinklers front and back, LOW taxes, NO HOA, newer HVAC and AC, water heater and double-paned windows, 2 sheds, Gated RV parking is approx. 30ft. by 9' 6" and the garage door opener has Wi-Fi capability plus HUGE savings on your utility bills with the SOLAR.  It's a short walk (.3 miles) to the Santa Ana River Trail and very close to the Hidden Valley Nature Center. If you love walking or riding your bike, THIS IS A HUGE BONUS! Get ready because this one will go fast!
